    "## 1. ElGamal : Vue d'ensemble\n",
    "\n",
    "**Bas√© sur** : Diffie-Hellman + chiffrement\n",
    "\n",
    "**Setup** :\n",
    "- Groupe $G$ d'ordre $q$, g√©n√©rateur $g$\n",
    "- Cl√© priv√©e : $x \\xleftarrow{\\$} \\mathbb{Z}_q$\n",
    "- Cl√© publique : $h = g^x$\n",
    "\n",
    "**Chiffrement de $m \\in G$** :\n",
    "1. Choisir $y \\xleftarrow{\\$} \\mathbb{Z}_q$ (√©ph√©m√®re)\n",
    "2. Calculer $c_1 = g^y$\n",
    "3. Calculer $c_2 = m \\cdot h^y = m \\cdot g^{xy}$\n",
    "4. Ciphertext : $(c_1, c_2)$\n",
    "\n",
    "**D√©chiffrement** :\n",
    "1. Calculer $s = c_1^x = g^{xy}$\n",
    "2. Calculer $m = c_2 / s = (m \\cdot g^{xy}) / g^{xy}$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 2. Impl√©mentation Simplifi√©e\n",
    "\n",
    "**Note** : Cette impl√©mentation est didactique. En production, utiliser une biblioth√®que cryptographique audit√©e."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "class ElGamal:\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    Impl√©mentation simplifi√©e d'ElGamal sur groupe multiplicatif ‚Ñ§_p*.\n",
    "    \n",
    "    ‚ö†Ô∏è Impl√©mentation √©ducative uniquement !\n",
    "    \"\"\"\n",
    "    \n",
    "    def __init__(self, key_size=2048):\n",
    "        \"\"\"\n",
    "        G√©n√®re les param√®tres DH (p, g).\n",
    "        \n",
    "        Args:\n",
    "            key_size: Taille du modulo en bits (2048 ou 3072)\n",
    "        \"\"\"\n",
    "        print(f\"G√©n√©ration des param√®tres ElGamal ({key_size} bits)...\")\n",
    "        self.parameters = dh.generate_parameters(\n",
    "            generator=2,\n",
    "            key_size=key_size,\n",
    "            backend=default_backend()\n",
    "        )\n",
    "        self.p = self.parameters.parameter_numbers().p\n",
    "        self.g = self.parameters.parameter_numbers().g\n",
    "        print(f\"‚úÖ Param√®tres g√©n√©r√©s\")\n",
    "    \n",
    "    def generate_keypair(self):\n",
    "        \"\"\"\n",
    "        G√©n√®re une paire de cl√©s (priv√©e, publique).\n",
    "        \n",
    "        Returns:\n",
    "            (x, h) o√π x est la cl√© priv√©e et h = g^x la cl√© publique\n",
    "        \"\"\"\n",
    "        # Cl√© priv√©e : x al√©atoire\n",
    "        private_key_obj = self.parameters.generate_private_key()\n",
    "        x = private_key_obj.private_numbers().x\n",
    "        \n",
    "        # Cl√© publique : h = g^x mod p\n",
    "        h = pow(self.g, x, self.p)\n",
    "        \n",
    "        return x, h\n",
    "    \n",
    "    def encrypt(self, message_int: int, public_key_h: int) -> tuple:\n",
    "        \"\"\"\n",
    "        Chiffre un message (entier) avec ElGamal.\n",
    "        \n",
    "        Args:\n",
    "            message_int: Message encod√© comme entier (< p)\n",
    "            public_key_h: Cl√© publique h = g^x\n",
    "        \n",
    "        Returns:\n",
    "            (c1, c2) : ciphertext ElGamal\n",
    "        \"\"\"\n",
    "        if message_int >= self.p:\n",
    "            raise ValueError(\"Message trop grand (doit √™tre < p)\")\n",
    "        \n",
    "        # Al√©a √©ph√©m√®re y\n",
    "        y = secrets.randbelow(self.p - 2) + 1\n",
    "        \n",
    "        # c1 = g^y mod p\n",
    "        c1 = pow(self.g, y, self.p)\n",
    "        \n",
    "        # c2 = m * h^y mod p\n",
    "        c2 = (message_int * pow(public_key_h, y, self.p)) % self.p\n",
    "        \n",
    "        return c1, c2\n",
    "    \n",
    "    def decrypt(self, ciphertext: tuple, private_key_x: int) -> int:\n",
    "        \"\"\"\n",
    "        D√©chiffre un ciphertext ElGamal.\n",
    "        \n",
    "        Args:\n",
    "            ciphertext: (c1, c2)\n",
    "            private_key_x: Cl√© priv√©e x\n",
    "        \n",
    "        Returns:\n",
    "            Message d√©chiffr√© (entier)\n",
    "        \"\"\"\n",
    "        c1, c2 = ciphertext\n",
    "        \n",
    "        # s = c1^x mod p = g^(xy) mod p\n",
    "        s = pow(c1, private_key_x, self.p)\n",
    "        \n",
    "        # s_inv = s^(-1) mod p\n",
    "        s_inv = pow(s, -1, self.p)\n",
    "        \n",
    "        # m = c2 * s^(-1) mod p\n",
    "        message = (c2 * s_inv) % self.p\n",
    "        \n",
    "        return message\n",
    "\n",
    "# Instanciation\n",
    "elgamal = ElGamal(key_size=2048)\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"\\nüìã Param√®tres publics :\")\n",
    "print(f\"   p (premier) : {elgamal.p} ({elgamal.p.bit_length()} bits)\")\n",
    "print(f\"   g (g√©n√©rateur) : {elgamal.g}\")"
   ]
