    "## 4. Propri√©t√© : Homomorphisme Multiplicatif\n",
    "\n",
    "**Th√©or√®me** : ElGamal est homomorphe multiplicativement.\n",
    "\n",
    "$$E(m_1) \\cdot E(m_2) = E(m_1 \\cdot m_2)$$\n",
